social_posts.post_text: Workin! Love from the #butchashop

It’s been a 30 year love affair with this music and culture. House music has been really good to me and to see this track-list and know that I’ve contributed and brought joy and happiness to so many just warms my heart. This track list represents so much hard work and so many sleepless nights but most importantly it’s my art and I am very proud of what I’ve accomplished thus far. I hope you all enjoy the music and the journey as much as I have 🙏🏽❤️

You can stream & download the sampler to my House Masters compilation via the link in my bio

#tbt throwing it back to a warm day last year with maestro Louie Vega. I just wanted to take a moment and say Thank you to everyone who has supported my House Masters release so far! The support at @beatport @traxsource, the DJ’s, at radio @petetongofficial @dannyhowarddj and streaming has been amazing and very humbling. I don’t take any of this for granted and I can assure you I’ve been keeping an eye on the charts and plays all week and that’s put a real smile on my face. Coming up next will be a stream with Defected that’s coming out at the start of February, recorded live at The Butcha Shop. Thanks also to @defectedrecords @simondunmore1 @seamushaji , to @inayaday @honeydijon , @louievega and everyone else who has worked on the project ☮️ ❤️ 🏠 music forever! And a special thx to my team @ralphusmoorus @puddy_uk for busting their butts on my behalf!

Prepping for tomorrow’s recording session with thee best vocalist I’ve had the pleasure to work with over the past 25 years. This has always been what it is about. Being shoulder to shoulder and working on the craft is something I do not take for granted. I’ve been blessed in so many ways and one thing I hold near and dear is my ability to create something from nothing. Something I’ve learned about myself is I only create when I have something to explore and bring to life. I stare at that virtual block of marble and I generally know already what’s inside. I’m blessed. So yes, it’s just a picture of a microphone but it’s definitely more than that. Stay tuned! #housemusic #studiolife #recordingsession

@harryromeroofficial is a House Master 💥

The legendary Jersey DJ and Producer, with an extensive back catalogue spanning two decades, has had his collection immortalised in the illustrious House Masters series ⭐️

The 34 track album includes a variety of Romero classics as well as some exclusive edits and remixes with the likes of @louievega, @honeydijon, @inayaday and @jamiejonesmusic! 

Deep dive into House history by clicking on the link in the bio and listening to the album in full 🔗

You can also listen back to Harry’s exclusive Defected Broadcasting House show on our YouTube channel now 📺

#harryromero #housemaster #defected #defectedrecords #househistory #housemusic #housemusicalllifelong

So happy to share this with all my producer, beat making friends. @wavesaudio has done it once again with their Magma tube channel strip. It’s been my go to since I was asked to create some presets for the product. I created 3 presets for your mixing needs. One for your kick-bass bus, your hats-shakers bus and lastly a preset for congas-bongos bus. OUT NOW!!! #WavesAudio, #WavesArtist, #wavesmagmachannelstrip

As we head closer towards Miami Music Week (which used to be known as Winter Music Conference!), this week I am flashing back to 2003 when I released ‘I Go Back’ with @this_is_robert_owens which caught the ear of everybody 20 years ago. I remember @joshwink1 @louievega @djkennydope @djtoddterry all reaching out and asking to do remixes. To say I was beyond shocked and flattered would be an understatement as I’ve been very public as to what those guys mean to me. Staying relevant in a career that has spanned 3 decades is absolutely mind blowing. Thank you thank you thank you! ☮️ ❤️

Thank you Mami for all your sacrifice, hard work, support and more importantly LOVE. I am the man I am today because of you. Thank for all the life lessons. Thank you for all your wisdom. Thank you for putting it ALL on the line for all of us. I will Live the rest of my life honoring you in EVERY decision I make. Please watch over us. Please keep guiding us in spirit as you did in life. My heart is broken but I know I will heal. I will miss you forever. Rest in peace Mami. Descanse en paz eterna. From your ‘Chinito’

Renowned for his Latin-inspired, percussive-driven house music, @harryromeroofficial remains a stalwart in New York’s nightlife scene. With recent hits like the ‘It Hurts’ EP and ‘Spirits III’ compilation, he now returns with the captivating ‘Mind Games’ EP in collaboration with @__shyam__p on Crosstown Rebels. 

The leading track Mind Games weaves a hypnotic groove alongside Shyam P’s magnetic vocals, while Mira brings in Romero’s signature blend of organic percussion and Latin vocals. Analog Bugz rounds out the EP with its powerful, no-nonsense energy, cementing Romero’s position at the forefront of the genre

Listen now through the link in bio
